## 3. Day-to-day commands (Makefile / justfile / npm scripts)

Single source of truth для common operations. Каждая команда должна работать standalone:

```makefile
# Makefile example (адаптируется под stack)

setup:       ## One-time dev setup
	scripts/setup-dev.sh

dev:         ## Start dev server with hot reload
	<stack-specific dev command>

test:        ## Run all tests
	<stack-specific test runner>

test-watch:  ## Run tests in watch mode
	<watch flag>

lint:        ## Run all linters
	<linters>

fmt:         ## Format code (in place)
	<formatters>

typecheck:   ## Run type checker
	<type checker>

db-migrate:  ## Apply DB migrations
	<migration command>

db-seed:     ## Seed dev DB
	<seed command>

db-reset:    ## Reset dev DB (DESTRUCTIVE)
	<reset>

clean:       ## Remove generated files
	<clean>
```

**Discoverability:** `make help` (или `just --list` / `npm run`) показывает все targets с descriptions.

**Никаких** «do X via this 5-step procedure» в README — всё через `make <target>`.

