## 5. IDE / Editor recommendations

**`.editorconfig`** в repo root — universal baseline:

```ini
root = true

[*]
indent_style = space
indent_size = 2
end_of_line = lf
charset = utf-8
trim_trailing_whitespace = true
insert_final_newline = true

[*.{py,go,rs}]
indent_size = 4

[Makefile]
indent_style = tab
```

### 5.1. VS Code (popular default)

`.vscode/settings.json` (committed) — shared baseline:

```json
{
  "editor.formatOnSave": true,
  "editor.codeActionsOnSave": {
    "source.fixAll": "explicit",
    "source.organizeImports": "explicit"
  },
  "files.trimTrailingWhitespace": true,
  "files.insertFinalNewline": true,
  "files.eol": "\n"
}
```

`.vscode/extensions.json` — recommended extensions per stack:

```json
{
  "recommendations": [
    "<stack-specific extension IDs>"
  ]
}
```

### 5.2. JetBrains IDEs

`.idea/codeStyles/` committed (project-level style settings). NOT committing user-local `.idea/workspace.xml`.

### 5.3. Vim / Neovim / Emacs

