## 7. Dependency management

### 7.1. Update routine

См. `dependency-policy.md` (отдельный artefact). Краткие правила:

- **Security patches (CVE) — automerge** если CI green (Dependabot / Renovate config)
- **Patch versions (no CVE) — weekly review + merge** if no breakage
- **Minor versions — biweekly review** + manual merge after smoke test
- **Major versions — quarterly evaluation** + dedicated PR с migration plan

### 7.2. Local update workflow

```sh
make deps-outdated   # show outdated deps
make deps-update     # interactive update (asks per package)
make deps-audit      # security audit (npm audit / pip-audit / cargo audit / etc)
```

### 7.3. Lockfile discipline

- `package-lock.json` / `pnpm-lock.yaml` / `poetry.lock` / `Cargo.lock` / `go.sum` — **always committed**
- CI verifies lockfile consistency (`pnpm install --frozen-lockfile`)
- Merge conflicts in lockfile — regenerate from scratch (delete + reinstall), не manual edit

