## 8. Profiling + performance debugging

### 8.1. Frontend (web)

- **Lighthouse CI** в GitHub Actions — performance budget per PR
- **WebPageTest / Calibre** для periodic deep dives
- React DevTools Profiler / Vue DevTools для component-level
- Chrome DevTools Performance tab для render bottlenecks

### 8.2. Backend

- **k6 / Vegeta / Apache Bench** для load testing
- **pprof** (Go) / **cProfile** (Python) / **flamegraph** (Rust) для CPU profiling
- **pg_stat_statements** + slow query log для DB-level
- Distributed tracing (OpenTelemetry / Jaeger / Datadog APM)

### 8.3. Performance budget

